title: Rodolphe Roche
text: Rodolphe Roche (born 14 June 1979) is a French former professional <a href="association%20football">football</a> who played as a <a href="goalkeeper%20%28association%20football%29">goalkeeper</a>. During his 18-year playing career, he represented <a href="EDS%20Montlu%C3%A7on">Montluçon</a>, Châteauroux, <a href="Le%20Mans%20UC72">Le Mans</a>, <a href="FC%20Saint-Louis%20Neuweg">Saint-Louis Neuweg</a>, <a href="Chamois%20Niortais%20F.C.">Chamois Niortais</a> and <a href="LB%20Ch%C3%A2teauroux">Châteauroux</a>.
